messages.content: I'll take this room 😀👍))
You're welcome to it!  Last we saw Zahir, he was recovering in the RV, watching Max and the old woman chat at the kitchen table

Okay ! 
So Zahir decides to look around the room, trying to process where he is and what's going on.
Did you see Jeremiah's post where he showed links to what the RV would look like inside?
Yep !

Ok.  It's quiet inside the vehicle, Max and the woman were talking quietly.  Moonshine and Becca stepped outside.  It's homely in a way that a hunter's cabin would be - there are a few gutted rabbits hanging up, some skins, etc.
Alright, so then Zahir thinks that Max and the woman are busy with something so he decides to look around the vehicle, seeing whats in there because of curiosity

It has the standard RV stuff (bunks, another larger bed, bathroom, kitchen, sofa, etc.).  A locked closet, and some clothes.  Nothing too out of the ordinary otherwise.  You have to squeeze past Max and the woman to explore
Alrighty, so after looking around the area, he decides to go over to Max and the woman to see what they're up to
And for that, we'll hold off until Max starts chatting.  I'll let you know!
Alrighty !
Join us in #rp3 for the conversation in progress.
Alrighty !
Why do I feel like when Zahir went to go find Becca he would end up getting lost ? .<.))
Seems like he's ok actually
That's good
Zahir is walking through the tents and RVs and starts walking past a small, out of the way tent.  He hears a familiar voice.  I'll roll INT plus Survival
Dice: 9,6,8,2 Successes: 2
He recognizes the voice.
The tent is in front of him, he's not close enough to see into it.  He hears Peregrine inside speaking to someone he can't identify.
He found Peregrine!!)
Zahir walks over to the tent and secretly tries to listen in on the conversation without being seen
I will roll Dex plus Stealth
Alrighty!
Dice: 6,9,2,3,9 Successes: 2
He's sneaky.
Transcript of the conversation:

Peregrine: Is sitting cross legged on the floor, there is no one else in the tent *sighs* "I know, Sal. I'm sorry.  I'm doing everything I can to atone.  Right now, the pressure is beyond anything I've ever dealt with.  Being AWOL is the least of my concerns."

Disembodied Voice:  "Being AWOL is a big deal.  Add to that murder, assault on an officer, and the fact that you lost our other friends - how could you possibly expect me to rest quietly?!"  *the voice is agitated*
Peregrine:  *deep breath* "I know.  If you think you're angry, I'm more angry.  If you're disappointed, I'm more disappointed.  But I'll *figure* it out.  Let me deal with it.  I have to go soon."
Disembodied Voice: "You had better deal with it.  Or I'll come back there and deal with it for it.  You killed Max.  I won't let you lose his sister too."
*She looks like she's getting read to stand up*
"Wait..they killed Max, Max has a sister?" Zahir notices that she might be exiting the tent soon and tries to hide outside to avoid being noticed
_...the dice clatter across the table..._
Uh oh
*Failure*  Peregrine sees Zahir when she exits the tent.
She immediately shifts from a human into a slightly more beastly form, like mostly human but also partially wolf.  She roars "What did you hear??"
Zahir starts to shake nervously "I uh..I got lost and uh..I tripped. Yea...and I uh. Yea...I didn't mean to stumble in here..yea..."
Peregrine:  *stares into his eyes and growls*  "I don't have time for you right now, but I will later.  And I will find you.  Don't be here."
She stalks off, in the same form.
Zahir, now terrified, attempts to run off, now panicking and anxious
Zahir and Max run into each other at full run.  Dex checks for both
_...the dice clatter across the table..._
_...the dice clatter across the table..._
Zahir falls to the ground.
Max stays up
Of course he does 😀👍
GG @Deleted User, you just advanced to level 9!
"Zahir!" His voice is so loud it draws others attention as he gathers the other into his arms. "Zahir, are you okay?!"

Zahir was a nervous wreck and full of anxiousness "IACCIDENTLYFOUNDTHETENTWHERETHATGIRLWASANDSHESAWMEANDSHESAIDSHESGONNADEALWITHMELATERANDIMGONNADIEEEE!!" He was shaking in fear of what could happen to him
"Zahir! Z, hey, calm down. Look at me buddy." Max takes Zahir's face into his hands.
Zahir was breathing really fast as he looked up at Max "I'M GONNA BE MURDERED!!"
Zahir does a Resolve+Composure check to get himself under control
(Am I in here now?)
_...the dice clatter across the table..._
"Z. Look at me. Name five things you can see."
Zahir is, barely, able to breath.  Otherwise, with the exception of Moonshine, I'll be picking up for you three on Friday

"Uh..you..trees..tents..weapons..I can still see that monster like thing in my head.. yea."
"Good. Four things you can hear."
" I'm too young to die Max. ;<;" Zahir was struggling to breathe a little due to the sheer fear he might soon meet his demise
"Z. Four things you can hear." Max's voice made no room for arguments.
"Uh...you..birds..the wind..and other people talking.."
"Okay. Three things you can smell"
"Uh..blood.. water..and smoke."
"Great. You're doing amazing buddy. Two things you can feel."
"Uhhh..the grass...and my stun gun.."
"Okay, last one: one thing you can taste."
"Uhh..do those rabbit from earlier count.?"
He nodded.
"Okay..then that."
((For the record, Max would almost certainly have gotten training on this via the Army))
"Good job. You did great Zahir. Can I give you a hug?"
Yep))
Zahir nodded
((The three would notice that more and more werewolves are walking past them to the center.  Nearly all are carry a lantern))
Max wrapped his arms around the smaller and hugged him gently. "There we go. You're going to be okay. No one is going to hurt you."
Zahir saw the werewolves and got even more anxious
((They'er completely ignoring the three))
Zahir calmed down a little bit seeing they weren't paying attention to them "Okay...maybe I overrated.."

Max chuckled lightly, the first time he's ever laughed around any of them. It's rich and warm, and he pulls away to look down at Zahir with a genuine smile. "Don't worry. Whoever tries anything will have to get through m- all four of us. You're not going to get hurt anytime soon."
((There are few werewolves left.  The stragglers are moving quickly))
That's a wrap folks.
